'https://api.github.com/users/vivek-microsoft/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}, 'body': '**Description**<!--Mandatory-->
allow the following params to take empty lists: 
--external-seed-nodes
--external-gossip-certificate
--client-certificate

**Testing Guide**
az managed-cassandra cluster update --client-certificate "path/to/cert/file.pem" -c cluster-name -g group-name --debug
az managed-cassandra cluster update --client-certificate "" -c cluster-name -g group-name --debug

az managed-cassandra cluster update --external-gossip-certificate "path/to/cert/file.pem" -c cluster-name -g group-name --debug
az managed-cassandra cluster update --external-gossip-certificate "" -c cluster-name -g group-name --debug

az managed-cassandra cluster update --external-seed-nodes "12.12.12.12" -c cluster-name -g group-name --debug
az managed-cassandra cluster update --external-seed-nodes "" -c cluster-name -g group-name --debug

**History Notes**
